strings.Value: "I saw what a terrible blow you suffered in that fight. Are you sure you're all right?"
"It's not often that one gets to see a walking corpse so close... And one that's barely standing, at that. You should heal yourself, or whatever you call it."
"I'm sorry, Jaethal. You were... gravely wounded today. Several times. They knocked the living daylights out of you! Ah, ha, ha, ha, ha!"
"I'm sorry, but your wounds... They still haven't healed. It's a horrible sight, but I can't look away."
"I wait when you become deadmeat. Dead deadmeat. Soon."
